<p>HOLY SHIT BALLS!? MOLEY ISN'T DEAD?!</p>
<hr />
<p>Please note that these rules are currently under construction so please bear with them and highlight any errors you can find in sections not marked <em>INCOMPLETE</em>.</p>
<p>Please note that this game is being created to be marketable to people outside of the wiki so suggestions for ease of play or clearer wordings are much appreciated but complaints that the game is too kiddy-fied help no-one unless you have actual proof the simplicity harms the game.</p>
<p>This page will also be used as the Rule reference document for the duration of the game's development and life. Please treat it as such and keep edits to a minimum. Also there will be sections that aren't needed to be completed until the game is in a presentable state but they will be added here for sake of completeness.</p>
