<h1 id="toc52"><span>Section 9: Thanks, Acknowledgements and Questions</span></h1>
<h2 id="toc53"><span>Section 9a: Thanks</span></h2>
<p>I need to thank the following people for help getting the SCP-CCG off the ground:</p>
<h2 id="toc54"><span>Section 9b: Acknowledgements</span></h2>
<p><em>this section will contain legal acknowledgements for all names and creations used within this project</em></p>
<h2 id="toc55"><span>Section 9c: Questions?</span></h2>
<p>If you have any questions or ideas about the SCP-CCG please drop them in this pages discussion or chat with me on IRC or in the SCP-CCG channel I often set up. Just type /join #SCP-CCG when you're using the realtime chat.</p>
